        <p class="text-accent font-heading text-lg tracking-wide mb-2">POCKET DOOR BLOG</p>
        <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-6xl tracking-wide mb-4">5 Signs Your Pocket Door Rollers Need Replacing</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Published March 24, 2026 · 8 min read</p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mt-4">
          <img src="/images/ilan-profile.webp" alt="Ilan - Pocket & Commercial Door Expert" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full object-cover" />
          <div>
